image-center\" alt=\"french-bakery-banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654509/french-bakery-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758108112326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599654509/french-bakery-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758108112326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"541\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"603947098\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"french-bakery-banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599654509\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"9\" data-media-id=\"b116fafd-1920-4570-99d8-3df0bbbf8786\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654509/french-bakery-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758108112326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654509/french-bakery-banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758108112326&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"m1vjb0or6y\">Project</span></strong>:  Creating a French Bakery</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"w0hkgx7g1b\">Created &amp; Written by</span></strong>: Marion Machelard, Emma Siret, and C&eacute;line Soubrane</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>It's 7 am. Dawn covers the shop windows and pastry in golden light. The smell of warm bread fills the room. The first croissants come out of the oven... Nothing better to start a good day than the French way, of course! Enter this immersive scene where rustic charm and traditional French craftsmanship come to life.</p><hr /><h1 id=\"Tutorials-Tutorials\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"tmdjehguss\">Tutorials</span></strong></h1></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/562823215/The+Hunted\" data-linked-resource-id=\"562823215\" data-linked-resource-version=\"34\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"thehunted.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599654509/thehunted.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758267004046&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599654509/thehunted.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758267004046&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607813662\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"thehunted.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599654509\" data-linked-resource-container-versi